# In the Curriculum: Career Journeys

## What are Career Journeys?

#### To help students see the real-world applications of computer science and music, we've included Career Journeys in the curriculum. Each lesson features a real professional from the music or tech world, helping students see themselves in these creative careers.

## Careers in the Curriculum 
